additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: 80 washes. ALL MACHINE TYPES. Australian Made. NP logo KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN FOR MEDICAL ADVICE CALL 131 126. USE ONLY AS DIRECTED HAND & SKIN CARE - After use, rinse and dry hands thoroughly. - If skin is sensitive or damaged, avoid contact with the liquid or wash solution. - For handwashing wear gloves. IF SWALLOWED - Remove as much product as possible from the mouth - Rinse mouth with water - Seek medical advice DAMAGING TO EYES - If product comes in contact with eyes, immediately flush with water for at least 15 minutes - Seek medical advice..
